The paper deals with the security and storage of passwords, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the challenges of securely storing and accessing passwords, which could fall under the categories of cryptography and security and privacy (cs.CY, cs.SI). The paper also presents a solution that involves data structures and algorithms for managing password backups, which could fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
